            <lg xml:id="TK480">
<l>uḷavarai tūkkāta voppura vāḷaṉ</l>
<l>vaḷavarai vallaik keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The measure of his wealth will quickly perish, whose liberality weighs not the measure of his property.</l>
